Get whichever Gandalf you can out first. I am thinking of adding an Albert Dreary and Barlin Butterbur but I am not sure where. Use Intimidate incase anyone wants to fight Sam and Merry, and make sure Merry has a Hobbit Sword. Hobbit Stealth Frodo Sam and Merry. Usually use Servant and Glamdring against the big guys like Balrog, Witch King, Cave Troll and Lurtz.<br />
